100% Cow's Milk: Bear Brand Sterilized Milk is made from pure cow's milk, providing essential nutrients naturally found in dairy. Sterilized through UHT Process: The milk undergoes Ultra-High Temperature (UHT) treatment, effectively killing bacteria and microorganisms. This process allows the milk to be stored at room temperature for an extended period until the pack is opened, ensuring freshness and safety.
Ingredients 100% Cow's Milk
Type of Milk • Sterilized Milk
Ideal For • Health-conscious individuals, families, and children who need a reliable and convenient source of calcium and essential nutrients.
Allergen Information • Contains milk and milk products.
Storage Instructions • Store at room temperature before opening. Once opened, refrigerate and consume within 3 days for the best quality and taste.
Where You Can Buy • Available in major supermarkets such as SM Supermarket, Robinsons Supermarket, Metro Supermarket, Puregold, and convenience stores like 7-Eleven and Ministop, as well as online grocery platforms operating in Cebu City.
______________________________________________________________________________
Nutritional Fact Energy: ~140-145 calories Protein: ~6 grams Fat: ~8 grams Carbs: ~11-12 grams (sugars are natural lactose) Key Nutrients: High in Calcium, also contains B Vitamins and Zinc.
